		"description": "<p>You become adept at ensuring those you are hunting do not escape. Once per turn at your option, you can spend 1 exertion to gain one of the following benefits until the end of the turn:</p><ul><li><p>Triple the range of any thrown weapon you use</p></li><li><p>Increase&nbsp; the DC of non-lethal poisons you create by 2 points (to a maximum of your maneuver DC)</p></li><li><p>Gain&nbsp; advantage on Perception and Investigation checks to find secret doors or compartments, concealed weapons, and creatures attempting to hide from you with Stealth.</p></li></ul>",
